- any uncontrollable mutations?
- Taking any questions.

104
00:04:07,710 --> 00:04:10,430
- Will there be more victims?
- Bureau operation, please stand back.

105
00:04:10,690 --> 00:04:11,816
Bureau operation, please stand back.

106
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,840
Stand back!

107
00:04:13,130 --> 00:04:14,250
Please answer our questions!

108
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:15,936
- Please stand back!
- Please answer our questions!

109
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,936
- Yeah.
- Please answer our questions!

110
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:18,200
Thank you for your cooperation.

111
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,186
Stand back!

112
00:04:19,210 --> 00:04:20,147
Please answer our questions!

113
00:04:20,171 --> 00:04:22,126
Have the Affinity B
infected lost their humanity?

114
00:04:22,150 --> 00:04:23,016
Over here!

115
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,766
Please answer our questions!

116
00:04:23,790 --> 00:04:24,186
Over here!

117
00:04:24,210 --> 00:04:25,210
Please stand back!

118
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:27,230
Bureau operation, please stand back.

119
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:35,750
Please answer our questions!

120
00:04:36,250 --> 00:04:37,470
Stand back!

121
00:04:37,790 --> 00:04:38,976
Please answer our questions!

122
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,760
- Please answer our questions!
- Stand back!

123
00:04:41,290 --> 00:04:42,057
Stand back!

124
00:04:42,081 --> 00:04:43,186
Please answer our questions!

125
00:04:43,210 --> 00:04:44,056
Thank you for your cooperation.

126
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:45,057
Can you please answer our questions?

127
00:04:45,081 --> 00:04:46,250
Go and check that.

128
00:04:47,210 --> 00:04:48,210
No filming or photos!

129
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:50,330
Over here!

130
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:51,807
What's going on?

131
00:04:51,831 --> 00:04:53,370
Don't tell me there's a bomb inside.

132
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,210
Sir, there's nothing inside.

133
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,057
He's staring at her.

134
00:05:12,081 --> 00:05:13,156
He's staring at her.

135
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:14,186
He's staring at that girl.

136
00:05:14,210 --> 00:05:15,556
Are you interested in this girl?

137
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:17,000
Are you in a relationship?

138
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:23,826
Please answer our questions.

139
00:05:23,850 --> 00:05:24,850
What's your relationship?

140
00:05:26,420 --> 00:05:27,500
Do you two know each other?

141
00:05:31,470 --> 00:05:32,726
- Hello!
- Please answer our questions!

142
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:33,846
Urgent notice from the bureau.

143
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:34,687
