159
00:06:53,961 --> 00:06:59,225
(Watch on www.kissasia.co, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

160
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:57,870
Hope all goes well

161
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,560
